<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.silver-shadows.com">www.silver-shadows.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Next, I just added a new forum to the Words of Shadow (our message board).  The new forum is called Tall Ales and Taller Tales (hence the title of this message!).  I just realized that up until this point, we had no &quot;official&quot; forum for our members to post roleplay stories, which I fear might have been discouraging some members.  <br>
<br>
Now we do have a place to share stories, and I extend this invitation to all who are reading this message.  Feel free to use it as a place to cross-post your stories if you would like to reach out to more members of the roleplaying community.  Many of our members only have time to read our board, and do not get to sites such as this.  If you have any stories to share, in particular anything that involves (or could potentially involve) the Silver Shadows, you are more than welcome to post here!  For your convenience, here is a direct link to the new forum:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fsilvershadowsfrm4">pub6.ezboard.com/fsilvershadowsfrm4</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Enjoy!<br>
